  "body": "Hi guys,\r\n\r\nThe speed is too slow when I query the api <debug_traceTransaction> on heco archive node, especially on the current block height. As Heco forked the base code from go version geth, not sure if it is because this version itself has perf issue when facing so big txs count and 3 seconds per block. \r\n\r\nIs there any other methods/apis to get the internal transactions rapidly? \r\n\r\nfor example, https://cn.etherscan.com/tx/0x10389012b0e122c9b1040871d1990fc8acccec72093a507a0e54366668fab432\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/34133322/116389839-ffa7c580-a84f-11eb-95c5-add0932c8e66.png)\r\n\r\n\r\nThanks,\r\nShirley",
